description: Returns a list of build versions for a specific workflow resource.

parameters.name: workflowVersionArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the workflow resource for which to get a list of build versions.

nested_items.name: workflowSummaryList
nested_items.description: A list that contains metadata for the workflow builds that have run for the workflow resource specified in the request.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the workflow resource.

nested_items.name: changeDescription
nested_items.description: The change description for the current version of the workflow resource.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The image creation stage that this workflow applies to. Image Builder currently supports build and test stage workflows.

nested_items.name: owner
nested_items.description: The owner of the workflow resource.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current state of the workflow.

nested_items.name: reason
nested_items.description: Describes how or why the workflow changed state.

nested_items.name: dateCreated
nested_items.description: The original creation date of the workflow resource.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
